Automatically starts barrier with the login screen and switches when screen is locked.

To install:

Edit barrier_lightdm.sh to replace IPs and such

Copy 70-linuxmint.conf to  /etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf.d/
Copy barrier_lightdm.sh to /usr/sbin/

Start barrier as the root user to add the SSL fingerprint

Restart the lightdm service
